snippet.title: Tactical Combat Department - Official 6 Minute Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
Tactical Combat Department on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1298010/Tactical_Combat_Department

Tactical Combat Department is a tactical turn-based strategy game inspired by Swat games. You command a special intervention squad that intervenes in various situations and environments.
